sys_update_xml.name: sysevent_email_action_c03f00150f3096005aad9259a1050ea0
sys_update_xml.payload:
falsefalsetruesc_req_itemtext/htmltravel.registration.validationfalsefalsefalsefalseeventfalseevent.parm1falseDear Traveler,

Your meeting/conference has now been approved by NIH/NCI. Registration for this conference can now be processed by our financial management team.

At this time, please review and validate the registration information submitted as part of your initial request. Please note that your registration will not be processed or paid for by the financial management team until all required information is uploaded to the request and until the “Validate” button is submitted.

To Validate Registration for ${number}:

1) Log into service.cancer.gov.

2) Locate the ${number} under My Requested Items > Open.

3) Review all information previously entered under the Registration Section and modify as needed. NOTE: This is the only section that can be modified at this time.

**Pay special attention to the dollar amount initially listed. This should be the actual amount that our Financial Management will need to pay when your registration is processed.  

4) Attach the following documents if not already submitted or if incorrect:

  • Approved CTPS/ STEPS snapshot
  • Completed Registration Form as obtained from the conference website (excluding the credit card information) - upload either a PDF or snapshot of this document.

Note: Usernames and passwords will no longer be accepted.

5) Click Registration Validation button located at the top and bottom of the page to submit request. NOTE: your request will not move forward until you select the Validation button.

Failure to submit the documents as listed above and/or to correct any outdated information for registration will result in a delay and/or denial of your request.

 

Click here to view and validate Request: ${URI_REF}

Requested for:  ${request.requested_for}

Opened by: ${opened_by} 

Opened: ${opened_at}


For questions please refer to the CBIIT Travel Hub on CBIIT Central.

 

 

]]>Travel and M+C - Validate Reg Infofalse100falserequest.requested_fortrue

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.TravelValiationReminder</api_name><client_callable>false</client_callable><description>Query sc_req_item to find out all tasks that are in "waiting_on_validation" stage and trigger events.</description><name>TravelValiationReminder</name><script><![CDATA[var TravelValiationReminder = Class.create();
TravelValiationReminder.prototype = {
    initialize: function() {
    },
	
	process: function() {
		var gr_requested_items = new GlideRecord('sc_req_item');
		gr_requested_items.addQuery('u_pending_reason', 'waiting_on_validation');
		gr_requested_items.addQuery('cat_item','960e56486f868a00e04fd15eae3ee41b');
		gr_requested_items.addActiveQuery();
		gr_requested_items.query();

		while (gr_requested_items.next()) {
		   gs.eventQueue('travel.registration.validation.reminder',gr_requested_items); 
		}
	},

    type: 'TravelValiationReminder'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>wuye@nih.gov</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-09-14 15:42:44</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>772f1a6a6fb16200bbc002e6eb3ee46a</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>TravelValiationReminder</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_772f1a6a6fb16200bbc002e6eb3ee46a</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>wuye@nih.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2016-09-14 15:43:43</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
